        "type": "paragraph",
        "snippet": "Effective couples therapy in Vancouver, BC, is widely available through evidence-based approaches like the Gottman Method, Emotionally Focused Therapy (EFT), and Relational Life Therapy. Key clinics include Wellspring Counselling, Open Space Counselling, No Fear Counselling, and Turning Point Therapy, offering in-person and virtual options for communication, intimacy, and conflict resolution.",
        "snippet_links": [
          {
            "text": "Wellspring Counselling",
            "link": "https://wellspringcounselling.ca/therapy/couples/"
          },
          {
            "text": "Open Space Counselling",
            "link": "https://openspacecounselling.ca/couples-therapy/"
          },
          {
            "text": "No Fear Counselling",
            "link": "https://www.nofearcounselling.com/best-couples-counselling-vancouver"
          },
          {
            "text": "Turning Point Therapy",
            "link": "https://counselling-vancouver.com/couples-counselling/"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "snippet": "Recommended Couples Therapists & Clinics (Vancouver)"
      },
      {
        "type": "list",
        "list": [
          {
            "snippet": "Turning Point Therapy: Specialized, evidence-based approaches (Gottman, EFT, Relational Life) with both certified and intern counsellors."
          },
          {
            "snippet": "Open Space Counselling: Focuses on attachment and communication styles to address infidelity, trust issues, and conflict, providing both in-person and virtual sessions."
          },
          {
            "snippet": "Wellspring Counselling: Provides tailored sessions for relationship navigation, particularly for high-stress or multicultural situations."
          },
          {
            "snippet": "Dr. Ross Dixon (Steadfast Counselling): Highly recommended for specialized marriage counselling in Vancouver."
          },
          {
            "snippet": "Best Marriages: Offers intensive couples therapy, including 6-hour daily sessions for couples in crisis.",
            "snippet_links": [
              {
                "text": "Best Marriages",
                "link": "https://bestmarriages.ca/what-we-do/intensive-couples-counselling/vancouver-bc/"
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "snippet": "Effective Therapy Approaches"
      },
      {
        "type": "list",
        "list": [
          {
            "snippet": "Gottman Method: Focuses on building friendship, managing conflict, and creating shared meaning."
          },
          {
            "snippet": "Emotionally Focused Therapy (EFT): A structured approach designed to strengthen emotional bonds."
          },
          {
            "snippet": "Relational Life Therapy (RLT): Targets fixing destructive patterns and regaining connection."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "snippet": "Common Concerns Addressed"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "snippet": "Vancouver therapy clinics often focus on:"
      },
      {
        "type": "list",
        "list": [
          {
            "snippet": "Communication breakdowns and trust issues."
          },
          {
            "snippet": "Infidelity and rebuilding intimacy."
          },
          {
            "snippet": "Life transitions (e.g., parenthood, divorce)."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "snippet": "Costs and Scheduling"
      },
      {
        "type": "list",
        "list": [
          {
            "snippet": "Rates: Generally range from $140 \u2013 $180 per 50-minute session for registered counsellors."
          },
          {
            "snippet": "Lower-cost options: Intern counsellors are available at some clinics (e.g., Turning Point) for reduced rates, often around $60."
          },
          {
            "snippet": "Format: Many providers offer both in-person Vancouver offices and online, allowing for flexibility."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "snippet": "It is recommended to seek out counselors specializing in the Gottman Method or EFT for high success rates in treating relationship distress."
      }
